<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>unless you can actually post some valid and not just large articles then I'm moving on<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Obviously no-one has to read any of the 'large articles' I have posted. The information contained in them seems valid to me, if by valid you mean intelligently and articulately argued, and based upon established facts.<br>
<br>
In considering Duncan's theory I have found I have been learning things I did not know before, and since increased awareness and education re. these weighty matters can only be good for us all in the long run, I would suggest that the subject has not &quot;passed it's use by date&quot;.<br>
<br>
